Actually this instructions don't say anything about blocking the game from the firewall, but blocking the firewall itself (i.e. turning it off). So yes, while squash34 is an idiot for making 4 posts in a row just to realize that the game works, you should come up with a better reason.

Anyway, game works fine except for a few control issues when sliding. But that's probably the game and not this torrent's fault.
